<!DOCTYPE html>
<html>
  <head>
    <meta content='text/html; charset=UTF-8' http-equiv='Content-Type' />
    <style>
      .email-body { font-family: 'Helvetica Neue', Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; background-color: #f4f7f9; padding: 40px; color: #333; }
      .card { max-width: 600px; margin: 0 auto; background: #ffffff; border-radius: 8px; overflow: hidden; box-shadow: 0 4px 10px rgba(0,0,0,0.1); }
      .header { background-color: #2d3e50; color: #ffffff; padding: 20px; text-align: center; }
      .content { padding: 30px; line-height: 1.6; }
      .details-box { background-color: #f8f9fa; border-left: 4px solid #007bff; padding: 15px; margin: 20px 0; }
      .footer { text-align: center; font-size: 12px; color: #777; padding: 20px; }
      .button { display: inline-block; padding: 12px 25px; background-color: #007bff; color: #ffffff !important; text-decoration: none; border-radius: 5px; font-weight: bold; margin-top: 20px; }
      h1 { margin: 0; font-size: 22px; }
      strong { color: #2d3e50; }
    </style>
  </head>
  <body class="email-body">
    <div class="card">
      <div class="header">
        <h1>Bug Tracker Assignment</h1>
      </div>
      <div class="content">
        <p>Hello <strong><%= @user.full_name %></strong>,</p>
        <p>You have been successfully assigned to a new bug in the project <strong><%= @project.name %></strong>.</p>
        
        <div class="details-box">
          <p style="margin: 0;"><strong>Bug Title:</strong> <%= @bug.title %></p>
          <p style="margin: 0;"><strong>Project:</strong> <%= @project.name %></p>
        </div>

        <p>Please log in to the system to review the details and start working on the fix.</p>
        
        <center>
          <%= link_to 'View Bug Details', project_bug_url(@project, @bug), class: "button" %>
        </center>
      </div>
      <div class="footer">
        <p>&copy; <%= Time.now.year %> Bug Tracker System</p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </body>
</html>
